{"tid":1856861,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iphone 8s 黑mon，想攞返裡面d 相","createTime":"2020-02-02T00:16:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T01:23:08.000Z","uid":199261,"like":0,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"c858544498a6a69f93094dff9c97e553eb4a3dcb","tid":1856861,"uid":199261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T00:16:47.000Z","msg":"幾個月前電話跌咗落地，mon 落地，爆晒，裂痕都幾深<br />\n初初個mon 仲有好少粉紅色光，而家已經全黑乜都睇唔到<br />\n剩係想攞返裡面啲相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身無用icloud<br />\n以前試過用線駁落電腦<br />\n但係係好耐以前，所以得一部分相<br />\n<br />\n跌落地之後即刻用線駁落電腦<br />\n仲用到web whatsapp。應該解到鎖，但係itunes 無彈出嚟，感應唔到，sync 唔到相<br />\n而家就再用不到web whatsapp 了<br />\n<br />\n而家電話有聲識震，打過去會聽到鈴聲<br />\n但係我解鎖唔到電話，所以接聽唔到，推測點按個mon 都已經再無反應 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身電話啲電應該放晒，但係又好似差到電，如果唔係點會仲有聲？<br />\n但係駁落電腦itunes 又唔彈出嚟..<br />\n<br />\n我見apple 授權維修中心話維修就要原廠設定，我唔想這樣，如果整返但係攞唔到相都無意思了<br />\n<br />\n想請教下仲有無機會可以攞返d 相？ 唔該各位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b7d8f424d3d79a3e7f859940cfce7402589009d","tid":1856861,"uid":16061,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T00:18:54.000Z","msg":"去先達整返個mon囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462c0b0ac3c17c0412abc180dcdd8464daf46843","tid":1856861,"uid":247894,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T00:19:12.000Z","msg":"乜iPhone 8有s版架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"843f080346f6b1cfd3c4dbc4da4df08084a24fcb","tid":1856861,"uid":199261,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"462c0b0ac3c17c0412abc180dcdd8464daf46843","tid":1856861,"uid":247894,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T00:19:12.000Z","msg":"乜iPhone 8有s版架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T00:19:36.000Z","msg":"sorry，